ADDITIONAL NOTICE:

NoEyes is designed as a blind-forwarder, end-to-end encrypted chat tool.
No warranty is made regarding the security, reliability, or fitness of
this software for any particular purpose, including but not limited to
secure communications. Use at your own risk.

The cryptographic primitives used (XSalsa20-Poly1305, ChaCha20-Poly1305,
X25519, Ed25519, BLAKE2b) are provided by the Python `cryptography` and
`PyNaCl` libraries. The authors of NoEyes make no independent security
guarantees beyond what is described in the README.

